reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish and Functional!

It's a perfect fit for my collection, and I can now proudly display all my favorites without worrying about clutter.One of the features I love about this bookshelf is the added drawer. It's an excellent space for storing smaller items like bookmarks, pens, and even some snacks. It's a thoughtful touch that makes the bookshelf even more practical. Plus, the drawer is hidden away, keeping everything looking neat and tidy.The Tajsoon 9 Tier Tree Bookshelf is not just a piece of furniture; it's a statement. It adds a touch of sophistication to my living space, and I've received compliments on it from all my guests. It's a perfect blend of style and practicality, making it an ideal organizer for any room.If you're a book enthusiast like me, I highly recommend getting this bookshelf. It's a must-have for anyone looking to organize their collection while adding a touch of elegance to their home decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice bookshelf - you'll need a screwdriver
reviews.reviewText: There is no drawer in this bookcase; it’s just a box at the bottom. Despite the absence of the drawer, this is a great little bookshelf and perfect for locations that need something that isn’t very wide. It was packaged securely to ensure it arrived undamaged and easy for one person to put together. It came with an allen type wrench to be used for most of the screws but you will need a regular screwdriver for the back of the bookshelf (see photos). There’s an anchor included to secure the top to the wall to make sure it won’t fall over. The bookshelf itself is very sturdy, the only detractor is that the screws show on the bottom box part. When assembling, pay attention to how the holes look (the bigger holes are the part where the screwheads wind up) and the sides with the random looking little holes, all go on the same side and wind up as the back side. The instructions mention only turning screws half-way until others in place but I didn’t need to do that until the very end when putting together the box/bottom. When assembling the bottom, it worked best to start all the screws and once they were all in place and started, go around and tighten them all up. This bookshelf made a nice addition to our collection of shelves for storing our books.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Looks great; holds a decent amount of books; sturdy on flat floor.
reviews.reviewText: I [RECOMMEND] this bookshelf. It is a different look for a bookcase and is great for more compact spaces.Pros:~Holds a good amount of weight~Compact and tucks into small spaces well~Easily paintable~A nice looking display/decor pieceCons:~Exposed screw heads, no screw covers included~Floor needs to be flat/level. Thicker/uneven carpet might be a problem_____This shelf took a minute to put together! Not the easiest thing I've ever put together, but the end result is very nice. I have a smaller version of this style of bookcase and was excited to see a larger version. I like the way the books display in a different pattern than traditional bookcases. The unit itself is very sturdy, and it comes with an anchor for the wall, but if you are not putting it against a wall and your floor isn't flat, there is a chance it will topple.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Such a Cool Bookshelf
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this bookshelf, because it was so geometrically cool. It took a little time to put together, but the directions are pretty straightforward and it comes with all the necessary pieces. The style of this bookshelf adds to the record of the room and makes it have a more modern feel. I got it from my office with my son thought that it would be cooler in his bedroom for his books. Would definitely purchase again. For the price and sturdiness it is worth it. I plan on getting a few more from my home.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars assembly is a pain, but worth it!
reviews.reviewText: Not going to lie, I struggled through half of the assembly by myself. I made it to the other side, and am happy with the result! All in all, came together very well, but you will need a screwdriver (not provided in tools). It would have been helpful to know which side of the board to have facing up/down.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Shelf for places with limited space
reviews.reviewText: I recently got this tree-style bookshelf with storage cabinets and it’s great for optimizing space with style. This book shelf comes with 6 shelves and 2 cabinets at the bottom. this unique design adds a touch of sophistication to any room. Its narrow build is perfect for those tight on space and provides ample room to store. Assembly was anywhere from 30-45 mins and the end result was both sturdy and appealing. The quality seems fair and can hold up a lot of books.
